high_descs: Back away from the table and turn left. Walk toward the island and make a left turn to the center of the room, turn right and stand in front of the stove.
Grab the plate next to the stove.
Turn left and stand in front of the stove and look up to the microwave above.
Open the microwave and place the plate in and turn the microwave on. Then remove the plate.
Turn left from the stove and walk toward the door. Turn left from the door toward the shelves.
Place the plate on the top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Warm the plate, place it on the top shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the nearest corner and make another left, and then walk to the stove.
Pick up the plate next to the stove.
Walk to the stove on your left.
Place the plate in the microwave above the stove, turn on the microwave, and then take the plate out.
Turn left and walk to the wooden rack on your left.
Place the plate on the top shelf of the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Place a hot plate on the wooden rack.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the counter then turn left and move towards the refrigerator then turn right and move to the oven.
Pick up the plate on the counter between the oven and the sink.
Turn left, move towards the wall, then turn right and face the microwave above the oven.
Open the microwave door, place the plate in the microwave, close the microwave door, turn the microwave on, turn off the microwave, open the microwave door, and remove the plate from the microwave.
Turn left, move towards the wall, turn left, move forward toward the refrigerator then turn right and move to the door, then turn left and move to the shelves in the corner of the room.
Place the plate in the center of the shelves' top shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved plate on a shelf.
